help.HELP\n_h or help_: That's this page. I hope it's helpful.
help._c or config_: Shows you Jordy's settings at the moment. This will be configurable. Soon.
help.SEARCH\n_s or search_:
Searches for images on Google.
The default page is 1.
Each page contains 10 images to scroll through.
help._p or page_: Changes the page of the current search.
help.SCROLLING\n_b or n / back or next_: Scrolls through the current scroll list.
help.\n_s or skip_: Skips ahead in the scroll list by X.
help.QUOTING\n_q or quote_:
Archives a message. Use this handy guide to know exactly what argument to pass:
Mention a user to quote their latest message.
Preface a Message's ID with 'i' to quote a message by ID.
Provide a phrase or word that was used in the desired message to locate it.
